r due to the effect of the friction term appearing in the\nequation of motion for dark matter particles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jul 2014 20:04:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Dec 2014 15:09:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
