 considered. Given the information the theorem\nrequires about the process, a much tighter bound cannot be proved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Jul 2014 08:42:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2016 15:09:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-28"}
